TEASER
EXT. SKYSCRAPER - SEATTLE - NIGHT (2368 NOVEMBER)
It is raining outside.
A man wearing black wind coat comes out of the door of a
skyscraper in a low-key way and walks along the street
hastily.
After a while, he enters a bungalows basement.
INT. BASEMENT - SEATTLE - NIGHT (2368 NOVEMBER)
As soon as the man enters the muddy basement, we can see a
broken robot laying on the table and a few people around it.
Except the robot has a torso and four limbs, it dose not
looks like a human at all and its face is composed by pieces
of iron sheet and wires.
ONE OF A FEW PEOPLE
I believe this is it.
He points to the center torso of the robot and looks to the
man. There is an reddish metal imbedded in the iron chunk.
The man wearing black quickly pulls out his gun out of the
pocket and triggers it to the robots head. Boom. After
that, he lights a cigarette and smiles.
THE MAN IN BLACK
Tell Frank. We are going to make a
decent fortune.
EXT. THE BUNGALOW - SEATTLE - NIGHT (2368 NOVEMBER)
At the same time, a more sophisticated iron robot is
approaching to the basement. Its body is equipped with
various weapons. The tiny LED light on his forehead shines
red light.
The strange thing is that while it is walking, it makes a
gesture of drinking water, bends its hand a little as if
holding a bottle of water and raised to the face, but there
is nothing but air in its hand. This act is like a mines
performance.
Although acting weird, it approaches to the basement.
2.
INT. BASEMENT - SEATTLE - NIGHT (2368 NOVEMBER)
Everyone in the basement looks thrilled.
The man notices a noise near the basements door and turns
his head towards it.
All of A Sudden. Boom, Boom, Boom...
Before anyone has realized, the robot enters the basement and
use its machine gun kill everyone in that room.
It lifts the broken robot from the table like a sack over its
shoulder, then causally walks out of the muddy, or bloody,
basement as if nothing has happened.
MUSIC CUE: Into Each Life Some Rain Must Fall by Ella
Fitzgerald.
As its back dissolved into the raining night sky, we can hear
the sound of police cars.
Into each life some rain must fall, but too much is falling
in mine...
END TEASER

Felix Wilson (29) -- talented saxophonist has long hair down
to his neck. He is at stage playing solo saxophone

crowd gathers around the stage.
Although he seems to be fully immersed in the music, a sad in
his eyes.
After finishing his performance, Felix sits by the counter.

J. You know what it is. The money I

their chips has been legally

At this time, a beautiful woman about 25 years old walks into

The bartender and the guest holds their breath, while Felix,

BARTENDER (CONTD)
Yes, yes, you might be right. She

Geez, Genors are human too. Dont

Felix feels lost of a second. He realized that he really
didnt love anyone in his 29 life, except one person. But he
dont know if that was love. When Felix was 9 years old, his
parents both dead by accident. He closed himself in the lower-
level apartment doing nothing but playing blues harmonica all
day all alone.
There is one girl in the neighborhood who always attracted by
his music. The little girl peeped little Felix through the
little window every time she walks by. Sometimes, she made
some compliments. Most of the time, She hummed softly to
Felixs music. Such relationship continued over a year. Until
one day the little girl never came by to the window again,
Felix felt like that his already incomplete heart has nothing
left.

EXT. NORTHWEST BLUES BAR - SEATTLE - AFTERNOON (2368
NOVEMBER)
The rain penetrates the tall buildings and windows into the
front of the blues bar. An android, human-look robot, stands
in front of the entrance.
797 -- designed and produced by Sunring company, owned by the
owner of the Northwest blues bar, it is a woman-like android
with golden skin. Every pieces of its skin including its hair
has been gold plated, and it wears a sleeveless sequined mini
dress.
The form of the two pupils in its eyes are not circle but a
golden sun radiating shape. It is the doorkeeper of the blues
bar. Although it is programmed to watch out for potential
threat, its major purpose is to attract guests. Thus, the
designer programmed it with the ability to do certain human
facial expression and gestures.
797 walks back and forth and looks around with its unique
empty eyes from time to time.
CLOSE UP: 797S EYES CONTAIN GOLDEN SUN RADIATING SHAPE.

little boys use she pronounce but most of people use it
pronounce to 797.

features than human.(background information)
They arrived the building for Cecis dance class. This is six-

EXT. MONUMENT VALLEY - NAVAJO NATION - DAY (1850)
A cowboy is riding his brown horse alone through the red
dirt.
Sam8 (25) -- Williams digital character in the game Red
Dirt. He wears a necklace, a tiny bottle filled with red
dirt, and equips with the finest guns.
A strong west wind hits his forehead as well as a piece of
sheet he is holding. On the sheet, there is a drawing of a
scary-looking old man. And below it, a series of number is
presented -- 4000 dollars. The cowboy is a bounty hunter.
Suddenly, a window pops out: New Mission Accepted
The left screen shows that Sam8 is an advanced player. After
finishing his next target, he will upgrade to the level of
fifty. According to the announcement of Red Dirt, only few
player globally are able to reach level fifty, and whoever
reaches this level will have rewards and special mission that
designed for them.
Folding the sheet back to his pocket, Sam8 whistles, and
start to play the song Red River Valley using his carryon
harmonica. He is going to his next target.
A green spot on his digital map shows that he is gradually
approaching to his target. He located that his target is in
the little stable not very far from him.
He gets off his horse quietly, walks lightly into the stable
and sees his target feeding the horse. But his target senses
the movement and pulls the gun out of his pocket. Sam8 walks
slowly against the wall , his target has started to shoot
indiscriminately with his gun. But Sam8 turns and jumps to
avoid all the bullets. Just in the nick of time, Sam8 found a
perfect shooting angle and took only one bullet to his
target. Nailed it.
The progress bar is speeding up. A window pops
Congrats! You are in level fifty now, among the best bounty
hunters in the game! Great ability always comes with great
responsibility.

15.

Sam8 looks down to the piece of information. It is just like

He follows the map and dissolves in the desert.
